  "description": [
    "COLUMBUS SCHOOLS TO OPEN AUG 28 Heavy Enrollment Expect ed By Superintendent W J Bolger Jr Whiteville Aug 22 All schools in Columbus county with the ex ception of those in the Whiteville Administrative Unit will open Thursday Aug 28 Bus drivers who will man the transportation fleet are taking their written examinations and road tests this week Principals making up the clas hed group are already on duty having reported a week ago In most cases teachers have been hired to complete the facul ties The faculty of the Tabor City schools is short only one teacher and this is regarded as representa tive of the general situation County superintendent W J Erager Jr has called a preopen ing meeting of Negro teachers to be held in Whiteville next Tuesday at 2 p m Teachers in the schools for whites will meet on Wednesday afternoon at 2 oclock A record registration ie antici pated this year and principals are concentrating upon securing a heavy enrollment on the first two days The normal temperature of the duckbilled platypus is lower than that of other mammals duenna STARK DRAMA ERROL FLYNN BARBARA STANWYCK i IN CRY WOLF Plus Donald Duck Shows"
